{"questionId":"12931","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"z = a + b{\\text{i}}\">\n  <mi>z</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>i</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{b}} \\in {\\mathbb{R}^ + }\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>b</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">R</mi>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arg}}\\,z = \\theta \">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arg</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>z</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find an expression in terms of <em>θ</em> for <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arg}}\\left( {\\frac{z}{{z - 2a}}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arg</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mi>z</mi>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arg}}\\left( {\\frac{z}{{z - 2a}}} \\right) = {\\text{arg}}\\left( z \\right) - {\\text{arg}}\\left( {z - 2a} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arg</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mi>z</mi>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>z</mi>\n  